with our television studios,

00:02:58.990 --> 00:03:01.840
Chris Carter, on the X-Files, you know,

00:03:01.840 --> 00:03:03.640
Jim Brooks on The Simpsons.

00:03:03.640 --> 00:03:08.410
They really taught me how
to understand storytelling

00:03:08.410 --> 00:03:10.150
and production

00:03:10.150 --> 00:03:15.150
and it led to a 26 year career at Fox. So,

00:03:15.460 --> 00:03:17.830
Netflix kicks off the streaming boom.

00:03:17.830 --> 00:03:21.250
It takes Disney six years to
get into streaming launches.

00:03:21.250 --> 00:03:24.580
Disney Plus in 2019 buys
Fox to try to catch up.

00:03:24.580 --> 00:03:26.530
